    <title>Java学习</title>
    <url>/2020/12/25/MyJava/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h1 id="多线程"><a href="#多线程" class="headerlink" title="多线程"></a>多线程</h1><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="class"><span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title">MyThread</span> <span class="keyword">extends</span> <span class="title">Thread</span></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="function"><span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="keyword">void</span> <span class="title">run</span><span class="params">()</span></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">        System.out.println(Thread.currntThread.getName() + <span class="string">&quot;正在运行&quot;</span>)</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>但是一般不这样用，使用Runnable接口，这样以后该线程还可以去继承其他类</p>
<p>如下：</p>
<figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="class"><span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title">Test01</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="function"><span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="keyword">static</span> <span class="keyword">void</span> <span class="title">main</span><span class="params">(String[] args)</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">        MyRunnable r = <span class="keyword">new</span> MyRunnable();</span><br><span class="line">        Thread t = <span class="keyword">new</span> Thread(r);</span><br><span class="line">        t.setName(<span class="string">&quot;张一航&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class="line">        t.start();</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="comment">// 模拟5秒</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">try</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            Thread.sleep(<span class="number">1000</span>*<span class="number">5</span>);</span><br><span class="line">        &#125; <span class="keyword">catch</span> (InterruptedException e) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            e.printStackTrace();</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="comment">//五秒后结束进程</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">        r.run = <span class="keyword">false</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="class"><span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title">MyRunnable</span> <span class="keyword">implements</span> <span class="title">Runnable</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">boolean</span> run = <span class="keyword">true</span>;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="function"><span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="keyword">void</span> <span class="title">run</span> <span class="params">()</span></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">for</span> (<span class="keyword">int</span> i = <span class="number">0</span>;i&lt;<span class="number">10</span>;i++)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">if</span>(run)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">                System.out.println(Thread.currentThread().getName() + <span class="string">&quot;--&gt;&quot;</span> + i);</span><br><span class="line">                <span class="keyword">try</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">                    Thread.sleep(<span class="number">1000</span>);</span><br><span class="line">                &#125; <span class="keyword">catch</span> (InterruptedException e) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">                    e.printStackTrace();</span><br><span class="line">                &#125;</span><br><span class="line">            &#125;<span class="keyword">else</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">                <span class="comment">//终止线程</span></span><br><span class="line">                <span class="comment">//save-- 保存数据</span></span><br><span class="line">                <span class="keyword">return</span>;</span><br><span class="line">            &#125;</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//这是一个终止线程的例子，更简单的唤醒线程使用Thread.interrupt();就行了</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p><img src="MyJava.assets/image-20201226233017626.png" alt="线程基本图"></p>
<p>线程调度方法：</p>
<p>​    实例方法：void setPriority(int newPriority) 设置线程的优先级</p>
<p>​            int getPriority()获取线程优先级；最低优先级1，最高优先级10，，默认优先级5</p>
<p>​    静态方法：static void yield()让位方法；暂停当前正在执行的的线程对象，并执行其他线程</p>
<figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">Thread.join();<span class="comment">//将改Thead加入到执行中，本句所在线程进入阻塞状态</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h2 id="线程安全是重点"><a href="#线程安全是重点" class="headerlink" title="线程安全是重点"></a>线程安全是重点</h2><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">synchronized</span>(<span class="keyword">this</span>) <span class="comment">//放入需要排队线程的共同操作对象</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<ul>
<li><p><strong>守护线程</strong></p>
<p>用户线程结束，守护线程就结束（main是一个用户线程）</p>
<p>守护线程一般是个死循环;用来备份数据的。</p>
</li>
</ul>
<figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p><img src="../images/MyJava.assets/image-20210102225839783.png" alt="image-20210102225839783"></p>
<h1 id="反射"><a href="#反射" class="headerlink" title="反射"></a>反射</h1><p><img src="../images/MyJava.assets/image-20210103131543280.png" alt="反射01"></p>
<p>class.forname导致类加载，导致类中的静态代码块执行。</p>
<p>实例代码块：new实例的时候执行。</p>
<p> <strong>如何拿到绝对路径</strong>（必须在src路径下）</p>
<p><img src="../images/MyJava.assets/image-20210103134938850.png" alt="如何拿到绝对路径"></p>
<p>利用反射创建类的优点：可以吧类名写在文件里，创建时候随意创建</p>
<p><img src="../images/MyJava.assets/image-20210105215633572.png" alt="image-20210105215633572"></p>
<p>是用资源绑定器：ResourceBundle.getBundle()</p>
<p><img src="../images/MyJava.assets/image-20210105220848999.png" alt="image-20210105220848999"></p>
<h2 id="通过反射给对象属性赋值"><a href="#通过反射给对象属性赋值" class="headerlink" title="通过反射给对象属性赋值"></a>通过反射给对象属性赋值</h2><p><img src="../images/MyJava.assets/image-20210107110806652.png" alt="image-20210107110806652"></p>
]]></content>
